public class DNF
extends Disjunction<Reason>

Convenience class to represent a Disjunction of Expressions taking the Disjunctive Normal Form (DNF). Its children must be a Conjunction of Parameters (which are terminal literals).

See Also:
Conjunction, Parameter, Serialized Form
